  <li>Decimal fraction issue: 0.1+0.2== 0.30000000000000004, convert to BigNumber if doing currency calculation</li>
  <li>Special Number: NaN (+"a"), Infinity(3/0), -Infinity(-Math.pow(2, 1025), js exponent range [-2^1024, 2^1024])</li>
  <li>bitwise shift >> << >>></li>
</ul>
